show grants for 'user_super_ungrant';
Grants for user_super_ungrant@%
GRANT SUPER ON *.* TO 'user_super_ungrant'
GRANT SELECT ON `hal_db`.`hal` TO 'user_super_ungrant' WITH GRANT OPTION
GRANT SELECT ON `hal_db`.`riel` TO 'user_super_ungrant'
GRANT SELECT ON `mysql`.`user` TO 'user_super_ungrant'
GRANT `role4`@`%` TO `user_super_ungrant`@`%`
当前用户具有SUPER权限（自身拥有的权限）
场景1：角色授予给角色
grant role4 to role_priv;
场景2：角色授予给用户
grant role4 to user_priv;
场景3：权限授予给角色
grant SELECT ON `hal_db`.`hal` TO 'role_priv';
grant SELECT ON `hal_db`.`riel` TO 'role_priv';
ERROR 42000: GRANT command denied to user 'user_super_ungrant'@'%' for table 'riel'
场景4：用户授予给角色
grant user_priv TO role_priv;


当前用户具有SUPER权限（自身没有拥有的权限）
场景1：角色授予给角色
grant role1 to role_priv;
场景2：角色授予给用户
grant role1 to user_priv;
场景3：权限授予给角色/用户
grant insert on hal_db.hal to user_priv;
ERROR 42000: INSERT command denied to user 'user_super_ungrant'@'%' for table 'hal'
grant insert on hal_db.hal to role_priv;
ERROR 42000: INSERT command denied to user 'user_super_ungrant'@'%' for table 'hal'
场景4：用户授予给角色
grant user_priv to role_priv;


当前用户未具有SUPER权限（自身拥有的权限，无grant option权限）
：权限授予给角色
grant select on hal_db.riel to user_priv;
ERROR HY000: The MySQL server is running with the --read-only option so it cannot execute this statement
grant select on hal_db.riel to role_priv;
ERROR HY000: The MySQL server is running with the --read-only option so it cannot execute this statement


